#: ../../N/netlag.rst:5
msgid "netlag"
msgstr "netlag"

#: ../../N/netlag.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../N/netlag.rst:9
msgid ""
"[IRC, MUD] A condition that occurs when the delays in the :ref:`IRC` network"
" or on a :ref:`MUD` become severe enough that servers briefly lose and then "
"reestablish contact, causing messages to be delivered in bursts, often with "
"delays of up to a minute. (Note that this term has nothing to do with "
"mainstream \"jet lag\", a condition which hackers tend not to be much "
"bothered by.) Often shortened to just ‘lag’."
msgstr ""
"[IRC, MUD] \\ :ref:`IRC`\\ ネットワークや\\ :ref:`MUD`\\ "
"上の遅延が、サーバーが一時的に接続を失ってから再確立するほど深刻になり、メッセージがバースト的に、しばしば最大1分の遅延を伴って配信される状態。(この語は主流派の「時差ぼけ(jet"
" lag)」とは何の関係もないことに注意。ハッカーはあまり時差ぼけに悩まされない傾向がある。)しばしば単に‘lag’と短縮される。"
